== About me
I received the B.S. degree in software engineering from Jinggangshan University in 2013. I worked for International Business Machines (IBM), ShenZhen Corporation as a java application developer in 2013. 
I received the M.Sc. degree in computer science from Harbin Institute of Technology, Shenzhen in 2018. Now, I am a PhD candadian in computer science from Harbin Institute of Technology, Shenzhen.

== Education & Acadmic Experience
- 2009 - 2013, Jinggangshan University, Software Engineering, Bachelor degree
- 2018 - 2020, Harbin Institute of Technology, Shenzhen, Computer Science & Technology, Master degress, superived by Prof. [https://faculty.hitsz.edu.cn/yeyunming Yunming Ye]
- 2023 - 2024, The University of Hong Kong, Research Assistant, superived by Prof. [https://www.math.hkbu.edu.hk/~mng/ Micheal.K.Ng]
- 2020 - now, Harbin Institute of Technology, Shenzhen, Computer Science & Technology, Ph.D. student, superived by Prof. [https://faculty.hitsz.edu.cn/yeyunming Yunming Ye]

== Research Interests
- Spatio-Temporal Deep Learning 
